Frequently Asked Questions

What is the significance of net worth certificate, and how does ProMunim help in preparing it?

ProMunim understands the net worth certificate as an indicator of calculated financial wealth and they prepare such certificates considering various regulatory guidelines and banking policies. The certificate helps individuals or organizations to assess their financial strength, which is crucial for various purposes such as loan applications, investor meetings, and mergers and acquisitions.

What are the benefits of registering a business under the Startup India initiative, and how can ProMunim assist in the registration process?

Registering under the Startup India initiative can yield rich benefits to a business, such as tax exemptions, easier access to funding, and other government schemes. ProMunim provides Startup India registration as an additional service and their expert team can guide businesses at every step of the registration process.

Why is GST registration mandatory for businesses and how can ProMunim helping in the registration process?

GST registration has become a necessary requirement for businesses to become legally recognized suppliers. Without registration, a person cannot collect tax from their customers or claim any input tax credit of tax paid by them. ProMunim provides the fastest service of GST registration on demand and can assist businesses in the entire registration process, making it hassle-free and convenient.
